SourceString: Wings from a large flying creature.
The blood of a resilient boarman champion.
A hollow fang from a monster.
The lingering soul of a ethereal being.
A small piece of ice from a large glacier.
Eye plucked from a hulking giant cyclops.
A hoof from an agile centaur.
A fragment of energy drawn from opposing forces.
The toughened hide of a wild boar.
A vile secretion from a giant leech.
A fin from a dead ichthian.
The heart of a living statue.
The intricate inner workings of an automaton.
Magical lava taken from a creature of fire.
Magical animated storm taken from a creature of lightning.
The thick outer shell of a monster.
The soul of a creature, tormented by Nemesis.
A disgusting glob of pus, blood, and bile.
